Polygon drawing from Espruino
-----------------------------

The function gfx_poly (in gfx/poly.c) was extracted from Espruino:
https://github.com/espruino/Espruino/tree/master/libs/graphics

It is Copyright 2019 Gordon Williams, Pur3 Ltd, and licensed under the
Mozilla Public License Version 2.0. See LICENSE.MPL for a copy of the license.

Small Changes to the coding style and changes required for compatibility were
made by Werner Almesberger.


Citrine logo
------------

The original image used for citrine.jpg was generated with Stable Diffusion 2.1
Demo:
https://huggingface.co/spaces/stabilityai/stable-diffusion

According to the License section,
"The authors claim no rights on the outputs you generate, you are free to use
 them and are accountable for their use which must not go against the
 provisions set in this license."

The AI model is covered by the CreativeML OpenRAIL++ license:
https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-2/blob/main/LICENSE-MODEL


